1
03:12:54,340 --> 03:12:55,340
Up it goes!

2
03:12:59,177 --> 03:13:00,344
That's it.

3
03:13:03,933 --> 03:13:06,143
I want this fortress made safe by sunup.

4
03:13:07,018 --> 03:13:08,561
This Mountain was hard-won.

5
03:13:08,813 --> 03:13:10,730
I will not see it taken again.

6
03:13:10,982 --> 03:13:13,107
The people of Lake-town have nothing.

7
03:13:13,359 --> 03:13:14,734
They came to us in need.

8
03:13:14,985 --> 03:13:17,444
They have lost everything.

9
03:13:17,697 --> 03:13:20,824
Do not tell me what they have lost.

10
03:13:21,701 --> 03:13:24,119
I know well enough their hardship.

11
03:13:25,538 --> 03:13:27,746
Those who have lived through dragon fire...

12
03:13:27,998 --> 03:13:29,206
...should rejoice.

13
03:13:30,543 --> 03:13:31,543
They have much...

14
03:13:31,627 --> 03:13:32,960
...to be grateful for.

15
03:13:38,301 --> 03:13:39,426
More stone.

16
03:13:42,304 --> 03:13:44,431
Bring more stone to the gate!

17
03:13:44,681 --> 03:13:45,723
That's it.

